182
00:10:43,605 --> 00:10:45,170
to ask you about quite a bit.

183
00:10:45,170 --> 00:10:46,690
And it's one of several skills.

184
00:10:46,690 --> 00:10:48,970
You'll have to connect
this with some kind

185
00:10:48,970 --> 00:10:50,330
