734
00:42:51,230 --> 00:42:53,140
That's when the
denominator is 0 here.

735
00:42:53,140 --> 00:42:55,800
And it goes all the way to pi.

736
00:42:55,800 --> 00:42:57,940
Swing around just one half-turn.

737
00:42:57,940 --> 00:43:03,610
So the range here
